    "title": "『信じる』",
    "enTitle": "I Believe",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『菊花賞』後――学校やトレーニングに出ず、\n無気力な日々を過ごすナリタタイシンは\nあるバスケットボールの試合を見て驚く。",
            "enText": "Following the Kikuka Sho, Narita Taishin<n>spends\nher days in a listless melancholy,<n>shirking both\ntraining and school—until<n>her spirits are stirred by\na basketball<n>game.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 123,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "pathId": -8325453976221429801,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "テレビの中で活躍するのは『皐月賞』前、\nナリタタイシンに厳しい言葉を\n投げかけてきた小さな赤髪の少女だった。",
            "enText": "She realizes that the young, redheaded<n>player on\nTV was the one who<n>confronted her before the\nSatsuki Sho.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 115,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": -4666500821838390546
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 268,
                    "pathId": 1165970888753696630
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": 4947240830399208311
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 327,
                    "pathId": -692124267809927513
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3360633635002287955,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ひねくれているが誰よりも強く、\n絶対に諦めない誰かから\n『諦めない勇気』をもらったという少女。",
            "enText": "The girl tells of how she received the<n>courage to\nnever give up from a certain<n>person—someone\nwho is stronger than<n>anyone she knows.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": 5048078901588100115
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 268,
                    "pathId": 1649300522228984028
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": -7094703106915187337
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 327,
                    "pathId": 7677398184840719335
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4497590977701610511,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "逆境に負けぬ強さを持つナリタタイシンに\n励まされ、奮い立たせられてきたと話す\nウイニングチケット。",
            "enText": "And Winning Ticket explains that Narita<n>Taishin's\nstrength to never back down<n>has always inspired\nand encouraged her.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": -2661188953801052467
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 268,
                    "pathId": 377170034790686156
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": -3134645121839384074
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 327,
                    "pathId": 4211868266685764323
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8716658432836786009,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そして、ナリタタイシンを信じ、\n復帰を毎日待ち続けたトレーナーからの\n真摯な励ましを受け――",
            "enText": "All this time, I never lose faith in Narita<n>Taishin\nand wait for her return every<n>day—until I finally\nget the chance to<n>give her some heartfelt\nencouragement.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 429,
                    "pathId": 5542934561471530443
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 208,
                    "pathId": 8299359997254759257
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 403,
                    "pathId": 6935610143847240487
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 327,
                    "pathId": 5616589374718046373
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4352328815201510322,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "諦めたくないという気持ちを取り戻した\r\nナリタタイシンは、\n『日経賞』でのリベンジを決心するのだった。",
            "enText": "She rediscovers her will to keep fighting<n>and vows\nto make a comeback at the<n>Nikkei Sho.",
